text: Lubor Knapp (born 3 August 1976) is a Czech football player who last played for Union Baumgartenberg.Baumgartenberg: "Abstand ist zu groß" ==Career== Knapp played for several top flight Czech and Slovak football clubs, including Baník Ostrava, Viktoria Plzeň and AS Trenčín.
